# Anomaly Detection & AI Analysis

**Owner:** Thomas Kamel

## Description
Analyzes normalized transactions for anomalous patterns and uses an LLM to generate a plain-English explanation of why each transaction was flagged, writing risk scores and explanations back to Airtable.

